The group also said that after more than 5,000 acts performed to improve nutrition for mothers and children in the UK, the government announced funds for a project, Power of Nutrition, which would reach 5 million women and children through nutrition.
Responding to one of the questions at the General Answers on their website asking "what makes you think we can end this extreme poverty?"
